'''Timett''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first]] and [[Season 2|second]] seasons. He is played by [[Tobias Winter]] and debuts in the &quot;[[The Pointy End]].&quot; Timett is the leader of the [[Burned Men]] and a renowned fearless warrior.

